  <h1>THE <span>SPLIT</span></h1>
  <p class="sub">9 weeks. New technique every week. Foundation → Intensification → Peak. Chest opens Monday and Thursday. Iron Cross closes every Monday. Complex + squats on Friday throughout.</p>
