<!-- OVERVIEW -->
<div id="ov" class="page active">
  <div class="stag">Block 2 Structure</div>
  <div class="note red"><strong>Chest is the priority.</strong> Chest opens Monday with full volume. Thursday always starts with a chest opener set. Iron Cross closes Monday every week — no exceptions.</div>
  <div class="note teal"><strong>The Iron Cross (every Monday):</strong> DB Incline → DB Flat → DB Fly → DB Pullover. One pair of DBs, no put-down. 3-sec eccentric every rep. 3 rounds × 8 reps each. 60 sec between rounds.</div>
  <div class="note"><strong>Friday Forge always:</strong> MMS Complex 3 rounds × 5 each (RPE 7) + High-Rep Back Squat 2×30 (RPE 7). Never changes regardless of technique week.</div>
  <div class="note"><strong>Abs:</strong> Mon, Wed, Fri every week. After lifting, before yoga.</div>
  <div class="wrow">
    <div class="dp ch"><div class="dl">Mon</div><div class="dn">CHEST</div><div class="df">Iron Cross</div></div>
    <div class="dp bk"><div class="dl">Tue</div><div class="dn">BACK+BI</div><div class="df">Iron Back</div></div>
    <div class="dp lg"><div class="dl">Wed</div><div class="dn">LEGS</div><div class="df">Abs</div></div>
    <div class="dp sh"><div class="dl">Thu</div><div class="dn">SHLD+ARMS</div><div class="df">Chest opener</div></div>
    <div class="dp fg"><div class="dl">Fri</div><div class="dn">FORGE</div><div class="df">Complex+Abs</div></div>
    <div class="dp rs"><div class="dl">Sat</div><div class="dn">REST</div></div>
    <div class="dp rs"><div class="dl">Sun</div><div class="dn">REST</div></div>
  </div>
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:8px">
    <div style="background:#eff6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:5px;padding:10px">
      <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;color:#1d4ed8;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:5px">FOUNDATION · WKS 7–9</div>
      <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8">
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 7 — Controlled Eccentrics</strong>3-sec lower every rep. Baseline loads.<br><br>
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 8 — Pre-Exhaust</strong>Isolation → compound, zero rest.<br><br>
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 9 — Drop Sets</strong>Final set only: drop 25–30%, max reps.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="background:#fffbeb;border:1px solid #fde68a;border-radius:5px;padding:10px">
      <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;color:#92400e;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:5px">INTENSIFICATION · WKS 10–12</div>
      <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8">
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 10 — Rest-Pause</strong>Max / 15 breaths / max / 15 breaths / max.<br><br>
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 11 — 5-Sec Negatives</strong>5-sec lower + stretch hold on final rep.<br><br>
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 12 — Giant Sets</strong>3–4 isolations back-to-back, zero rest.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="background:#fef2f2;border:1px solid #fecaca;border-radius:5px;padding:10px">
      <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;color:#dc2626;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:5px">PEAK · WKS 13–15</div>
      <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8">
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 13 — Cluster Sets</strong>1 rep → rack → 10 sec → ×5. 85–90% load.<br><br>
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 14 — Mechanical Drop Sets</strong>Fail → change angle → continue, same weight.<br><br>
        <strong style="color:var(--text);display:block">Wk 15 — Max Effort + Pause</strong>2-sec pause every compound. PR week.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

