    <div class="tn">Controlled Eccentrics</div>
    <div class="ts">Thibaudeau / General Hypertrophy Science</div>
    <div class="td"><strong>Rule:</strong> 3-second lowering on every rep, every set, every exercise. Explode up, control down. These are your baseline loads — what you establish here is the reference for all future weeks.</div>
